{"tid":191352,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗嘅朋友千其唔好去博愛動物醫院！","createTime":"2017-04-07T20:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T17:43:41.000Z","uid":80069,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f19b1f1b115a6fc3f08ea02cbecbf679601fadce","tid":191352,"uid":80069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T20:11:07.000Z","msg":"我隻雪橇離世就係因為個醫生鳩下鳩下唔識醫就唔好撚岀黎做累死人地隻狗，件事係咁⋯<br />\n<br />\n-有一日Husky右腳無拿拿跛下跛下我地就帶佢去黎間垃圾博愛，條友摸兩摸聽下就話佢拗到隻腳姐冇嘢嘅開啲消炎止痛藥就得㗎啦，我仲問就係咁簡單check完？佢就話仲有事就黎覆診....<br />\n<br />\n-點知無幾耐Husky就屙血尿我地去覆診問個醫生，佢抽下血驗下就話肝指數同紅血球偏低而白血球就偏高，我問咁即係點咩病食完反而有反效果，佢竟然答我唔知要寄返報告去外國問下啲專業人士，叫我地食住啲藥返去等下<br />\n<br />\n-隔左排血尿問題仲越嚟越嚴重Husky仲半夜痛到嗌，我哋即刻車去睇，條友竟然仲未check到仲R晒頭，最後佢搞唔掂轉介到太平洋醫院PAVC，先知原來Hucky患咗睪丸癌(內隱)重點係咩？重點係發現得太遲，癌細胞已經擴散到全身，冇幾耐就下半身癱瘓，要姑娘幫佢排便，住左一排醫院Husky好叻繼續撐到落去，但每次探佢佢都眼濕濕，佢好似話俾我哋聽佢覺得佢自己負累，望住佢我地好心痛好心噏，最後佢都係撐唔住，就係咁我哋Miss左一個拯救佢嘅機會<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/041050_0d8536340e6b2edafc96f97a009c6c24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F041050_0d8536340e6b2edafc96f97a009c6c24.jpg&h=32e45c41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad434af7511b63e2378854132f6aaa243e12ec3f","tid":191352,"uid":71470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T21:06:51.000Z","msg":"有養狗 心疼 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf98f9ebd3b010693cfa2cf731d1a4c9562b1818","tid":191352,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"佢呢間野好似成日都有負評"},{"pid":"eabe15f95d15037ea78bf1e70a22d600083f4857","tid":191352,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"個醫生咩樣㗎得大家識得避吓<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗狗都有cancer, 但係遇到好醫生<br />\n捱過左十幾次化療，依家都算健康<br />\n睇住隻狗辛苦好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435df0c8670a463b5e73c188a625a79f90f70358","tid":191352,"uid":80069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有養狗 心疼 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以千其唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f781f3ccace35560baba566bb0283283b22bfe3","tid":191352,"uid":80069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢呢間野好似成日都有負評</blockquote><br />\n後尾上網check過先知所以打後啲貓狗轉曬睇第二間"},{"pid":"9e3e5a3b12533adaea4e60de1953ae4464ad5b26","tid":191352,"uid":80069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個醫生咩樣㗎得大家識得避吓<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗狗都有cancer, 但係遇到好醫生<br />\n捱過左十幾次化療，依家都算健康<br />\n睇住隻狗辛苦好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你都好啲遇着個好，養左咁耐望住佢咁難受真係好心痛，個醫生有少量白頭髮，肥，戴眼鏡"},{"pid":"da6315443c7b4079b4ee515bb547054e0c83dbcb","tid":191352,"uid":99561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"噢...我隻狗都有隱睪....超怕佢會有cancer..."},{"pid":"fa97f49552a41eb94949383e852afd836d764c94","tid":191352,"uid":3519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"發覺香港地好多獸醫都好低質下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5968ac24a230dbf35344518894f647fd5356503d","tid":191352,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":