" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d941d44c8c16d65885218b966f664b632f4c44f","tid":191352,"uid":43171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>發覺香港地好多獸醫都好低質下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如share 吓有咩好獸醫</blockquote><br />\n而家睇開新界動物醫院<br />\n地址:元朗馬田路50號(馬田村牌坊對面)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/204647_f5a1e5b8bd48546863e3795e5a155417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F204647_f5a1e5b8bd48546863e3795e5a155417.jpg&h=2427b2f1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢間除左貴同24小時外 一啲都唔好</blockquote><br />\n每個人定義唔同姐你話唔好我就覺得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢間前排先有負評，啲醫生姑娘無乜愛心<br />\n<br />\n利申有陪朋友帶隻狗狗睇過，淨係識叫人做測試又斷唔到症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁奇怪，狗狗咩病斷唔到症</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係整損個嘴流咗好多血，但個獸醫就話「覺得」係牛痺熱，而驗血報告嘅指數唔支持佢呢個講法（佢自己講嘅），最後仍然堅持話似係牛痺熱叫我朋友再做多啲測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我朋友話食咗消炎藥睇下點先就攞藥走咗。最後食咗兩日藥無晒事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c21615aefbb31f93d55f66d22ef0b0bfb7a920","tid":191352,"uid":45526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n不如share 吓有咩好獸醫</blockquote><br />\n而家睇開新界動物醫院<br />\n地址:元朗馬田路50號(馬田村牌坊對面)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/204647_f5a1e5b8bd48546863e3795e5a155417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F204647_f5a1e5b8bd48546863e3795e5a155417.jpg&h=2427b2f1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢間除左貴同24小時外 一啲都唔好</blockquote><br />\n每個人定義唔同姐你話唔好我就覺得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢間前排先有負評，啲醫生姑娘無乜愛心<br />\n<br />\n利申有陪朋友帶隻狗狗睇過，淨係識叫人做測試又斷唔到症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁奇怪，狗狗咩病斷唔到症</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係整損個嘴流咗好多血，但個獸醫就話「覺得」係牛痺熱，而驗血報告嘅指數唔支持佢呢個講法（佢自己講嘅），最後仍然堅持話似係牛痺熱叫我朋友再做多啲測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我朋友話食咗消炎藥睇下點先就攞藥走咗。最後食咗兩日藥無晒事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我隻貓入屋時有耳炎 帶去睇照埋顯鏡話無耳蚤<br />\n但番到黎義工話我知佢就係開隻耳蚤油俾我<br />\n我個時新手養貓 我問應該要點處理滴藥同洗耳<br />\n佢係叫個護士教我 但佢全程唔係度 個護士教錯晒 <br />\n滴完14日都未斷尾 義工重新教我一次 再去到另一間睇先斷尾<br />\n<br />\n同埋我隻貓個時得0.6kg 仲係算過瘦 但個醫生都覺得仲可以打到針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3531eaa763e5de4c797d5354f24b73e0a7ac662e","tid":191352,"uid":80069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇下你隻狗狗係點既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/15/014054_9873fe9d01a6aa5a629c148605a20d4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F15%2F014054_9873fe9d01a6aa5a629c148605a20d4f.jpg&h=1716fa92&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}